47:27.857 --> 47:30.320
‐ And what position is this?

47:30.320 --> 47:31.698
‐ Chief of Police.

47:31.698 --> 47:33.242
‐ Really?! Where?

47:33.242 --> 47:35.330
‐ Leisureville.
‐ Jesus H., Keith.

47:35.330 --> 47:38.419
