We're contemporaries.

47:38.419 --> 47:39.672
‐ Can I help you with something?

47:39.672 --> 47:41.217
‐ Where's Veronica?

47:41.217 --> 47:43.179
‐ Amalia Maloof requested a visit.

47:43.179 --> 47:45.433
‐ Well, aren't you two popular today.

47:45.433 --> 47:46.268
‐ Are we?

47:46.268 --> 47:49.859
‐ Mm. My new client wants me to arrange
a meeting between the two of you.

47:49.859 --> 47:54.869
It's bizarre, but let's face it, the world
stopped making sense when Prince died.

47:54.869 --> 47:56.080
‐ Who's the client?

47:56.080 --> 47:58.042
‐ [ sighs ]

47:58.042 --> 48:01.800
‐ I deserve this... is all.

48:01.800 --> 48:03.469
I did bad things...

48:03.469 --> 48:05.139
‐ Ignore him.

48:06.350 --> 48:08.522
He's on morphine.

48:08.522 --> 48:11.987
Thank you again for catching the man
who maimed my son.

48:13.865 --> 48:16.412
‐ You should know we don't believe

48:16.412 --> 48:19.042
