50:05.506 --> 50:07.217
‐ What's up with you?

50:07.217 --> 50:10.599
The smiling. The warmth? I don't get it.

50:10.599 --> 50:13.479
‐ All in due time. [ kisses ]

50:13.479 --> 50:16.318
